text: Mössingen is a town in Tübingen in Baden-Württemberg in Germany. It is 13 km south of Tübingen. Mössingen is on the northern edge of the Swabian Jura in the valley of the Steinlach, a right tributary of the Neckar. == References == == Other websites == * Official website * Blumenstadt Mössingen Category:Tübingen (district)
